Package: rPackageSmall
Type: Package
Title: Small R Package with S4 Classes (rrlmgraph Benchmark Fixture)
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A small CRAN-style R package with S4 classes, generics, and
    methods, used as a benchmark fixture for rrlmgraph.  Tests S4 dispatch
    detection in the graph builder.  Not intended for independent
    installation.
